<title>Introduction</title>
<para>This module lists all the hardware accelerator implemented Crypto algorithms.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="index_1autotoc_md17">
<title>Crypto Operations</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>AES Algorithm which includes ECB, CBC, CTR modes</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Key Agreement Algorithm ECDH</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Digital Signature Algorithm ECDSA</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>AEAD Algorithms which include CCM, GCM, ChachaPoly</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Secure Hash Algorithm SHA which include SHA1, SHA224, SHA256, SHA384, SHA512 modes</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>True Random Number Generator</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Attestation token generation</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Message Authenticated Code Algorithm HMAC. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
